---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Card } from '../components/ui/card';
import Footer from '../components/Footer';
import { FileText, Download, Image, Mail } from 'lucide-react';
---

<Layout title="Press Kit - Summit AI Notes" description="Media resources and press information for Summit AI Notes">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-background via-background to-muted/20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <FileText class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" />
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">Press Kit</h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground">
            Media resources and company information
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- About Summit -->
        <Card className="p-8 mb-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-purple-50 border-blue-200">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">About Summit AI Notes</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
            Summit AI Notes is a privacy-first macOS application that records, transcribes, and summarizes meetings using local AI processing. Unlike cloud-based alternatives, Summit processes all audio and generates meeting notes entirely on the user's device, ensuring complete privacy and data security.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            Designed for professionals handling sensitive information—including consultants, lawyers, financial advisors, and healthcare providers—Summit makes it possible to leverage powerful AI tools without compromising client confidentiality.
          </p>
        </Card>

        <!-- Key Facts -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-foreground mb-6">Key Facts</h2>
          <Card className="p-6">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Platform</h3>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground">macOS (12+)</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Category</h3>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground">Productivity, AI, Business Tools</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Target Users</h3>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground">Consultants, Legal, Finance, Healthcare</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Key Differentiator</h3>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground">100% local AI processing</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Status</h3>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground">In Development (Accepting Waitlist)</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Website</h3>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground">summitnotes.app</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </Card>
        </div>

        <!-- Product Description -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-foreground mb-6">Product Description</h2>
          <Card className="p-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Short (50 words)</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6 pb-6 border-b border-border">
              Summit AI Notes is a privacy-first macOS app for recording, transcribing, and summarizing meetings. Unlike cloud-based tools, all AI processing happens locally on your Mac, ensuring client conversations and sensitive information never leave your device.
            </p>

            <h3 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Medium (100 words)</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6 pb-6 border-b border-border">
              Summit AI Notes transforms how professionals document meetings while maintaining complete privacy. The macOS application uses local AI processing to record, transcribe, and generate intelligent summaries of conversations—all without sending data to the cloud. Designed for consultants, lawyers, financial advisors, and healthcare providers, Summit enables users to leverage cutting-edge AI technology without compromising client confidentiality. With support for local LLM providers like LM Studio and optional cloud services, Summit offers flexibility while prioritizing privacy. Meeting recordings, transcripts, and notes stay encrypted on the user's device, under their complete control.
            </p>

            <h3 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Long (200 words)</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground">
              In an era where AI-powered productivity tools typically require sending sensitive data to the cloud, Summit AI Notes offers a different approach. Built specifically for professionals who handle confidential information, Summit is a macOS application that performs all meeting transcription and AI summarization locally on the user's device.
              <br><br>
              The application records audio from any source—video calls, phone conversations, or in-person meetings—and uses local speech recognition to generate accurate transcripts. An integrated AI system then analyzes these transcripts to produce comprehensive meeting summaries with key points, decisions, and action items. All of this happens on the user's Mac, with no cloud uploads required.
              <br><br>
              Target users include independent consultants, attorneys, financial advisors, healthcare providers, and any professional who needs to document conversations while maintaining strict confidentiality standards. Summit supports integration with LM Studio for completely local AI processing, as well as optional cloud providers (OpenAI, Anthropic, Google) for users who prefer that approach—though even with cloud providers, only text transcripts are sent, never audio recordings.
              <br><br>
              With encrypted local storage, customizable summary templates, and powerful search capabilities, Summit AI Notes makes it possible to reclaim hours spent on meeting documentation while ensuring client privacy is never compromised.
            </p>
          </Card>
        </div>

        <!-- Brand Assets -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-foreground mb-6">Brand Assets</h2>
          <Card className="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-6">
              <Image class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600 mt-1" />
              <div class="flex-1">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Logo & Visual Assets</h3>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
                  High-resolution logos, app screenshots, and marketing images will be available here once we're closer to launch.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
                  For immediate media needs, please contact <a href="mailto:hello@summitnotes.app" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">hello@summitnotes.app</a>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </Card>
        </div>

        <!-- Founder Info -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-foreground mb-6">Company Information</h2>
          <Card className="p-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Mission</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6">
              To prove that powerful AI tools don't require sacrificing privacy. Summit AI Notes demonstrates that professionals can have both cutting-edge technology and complete control over their sensitive data.
            </p>

            <h3 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Values</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-muted-foreground space-y-2">
              <li><strong>Privacy First:</strong> User data belongs to the user, not in the cloud</li>
              <li><strong>User-Centric Design:</strong> Powerful features shouldn't require complex setup</li>
              <li><strong>Quality Craftsmanship:</strong> Build software that works reliably and performs exceptionally</li>
              <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> Honest communication about what we do and don't do with data</li>
            </ul>
          </Card>
        </div>

        <!-- Media Contact -->
        <Card className="p-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-50 to-pink-50 border-purple-200">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <Mail class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3">Media Contact</h2>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
                For press inquiries, interviews, or additional information:
              </p>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-2">
                Email: <a href="mailto:hello@summitnotes.app" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline font-medium">hello@summitnotes.app</a>
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-4">
                We typically respond to media inquiries within 24 hours on business days.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </Card>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <Footer client:load />
</Layout>

<style>
  :global(.dark) .prose {
    --tw-prose-body: var(--foreground);
    --tw-prose-headings: var(--foreground);
  }
</style>
